msgctxt "QL_Hateno_SheikPad_PowerUp_Explain"
msgid ""
"If you provide Purah with <1.se_co>ancient components<2.re_co>,\n"
"she can use them to strengthen your runes.\n"
"\n"
"The Sheikah Sensor takes <3.se_co>three \n"
